import React from 'react';

const IconZap = () => (
  <svg
    version="1.1"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    role="img"
    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
    fill="none"
    stroke="currentColor"
    strokeWidth="2"
    strokeLinecap="round"
    strokeLinejoin="round"
    className="feather feather-zap">
    <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"></polygon>
  </svg>
);

export default IconZap;
